# EBS volume types

## SSD

### General purpose SSD  
balance between cost/performance
- gp3
provides baseline 3000 iops, max 80,000 iops

- gp2
provides 3 iops * 1 GB. Max 10,000 iops

 - usecases :- operatng system and sql database mysql, sql server

### Provisioned IOPS
